src:
Tårgas mot Hongkongprotest utan tillstånd
Hongkongpolisen avslog ansökan om demonstrationstillstånd. Men människor har ändå strömmat till Victoria Park för den 22:a helgen av protester mot regionens – och Fastlandskinas – styre. Protesterna möttes av tårgas från polisen.
02 Nov 2019, 09:15 by TT

text:
Tear gas against Hong Kong protest without permission
The Hong Kong police rejected the application for a demonstration permit. But people still flock to Victoria Park for the 22nd weekend of protests against the region's - and mainland China's - rule. The protests were met by tear gas from the police.
02 Nov 2019, 09:15 by TT
